<template>
    <post-item 
    v-for="list in lists" 
    :list="list"
    :key="list.id"
    @remove="$emit('remove',list)"
    />
</template>

<script>
import PostItem from '@/components/PostItem.vue';
export default {
    components: {PostItem},
    props: {
        lists: {
            type: Array,
            required: true,
        }
    }
}
</script>

</style>
